/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheStade de France, built for the1998 World Cup, has been repurposed at very little additional expense as the main Olympic Stadium.\", \"from\": 5943, \"to\": 6074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5955, \"end\": 5961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9150918029652009, \"rank\": 0.07326736841291735, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, the fact that the Colombes Olympic Stadium from 100 years ago is still in use, is a powerful symbol of responsible and environmentally sensitive sports infrastructure policy and planning.\", \"from\": 6075, \"to\": 6270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6110, \"end\": 6125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.999999998848125, \"rank\": 1.1518776546464991e-09, \"text\": \"Olympic Stadium\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Stadium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ruadh\\u00e1n Cooketeaches French at theUniversity of Galway.\", \"from\": 6272, \"to\": 6327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6320, \"end\": 6326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Galway\", \"score\": 0.9998763122150425, \"rank\": 0.00012366755938646924, \"text\": \"Galway\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Galway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Galway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The views expressed here are those of the author and do not represent or reflect the views of RT\\u00c9    \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 6329, \"to\": 6441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 6442, \"to\": 6532, \"entities\": [{\"b